The disbelief regarding its success will be short-lived. Its platform and offering are quite real, with a product that has a genuine use case. It's a no-brainer. Now, the question is: how long will it take for people to (1) realize its existence, and (2) believe in its potential?

$TKNFY will experience a slow, but steady grind higher over the coming few weeks. Early on, people will be reluctant to claim due to poor price action. As it performs better and better by the hour, those claiming and selling for pennies will slow the momentum, but...
